{"word":"ἐπάνω","slug":"ἐπάνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπάνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄνω\">ἄνω</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> with the basic idea of superiority<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of place <b>above, over, on <a href='B:470 2:9'>Mt 2:9</a>; <a href='B:470 5:14'>5:14</a>; <a href='B:470 21:7'>21:7</a>; <a href='B:470 23:18'>23:18</a>; <a href='B:470 27:37'>27:37</a>; <a href='B:490 4:39'>Lk 4:39</a>; <a href='B:490 10:19'>10:19</a>; <a href='B:730 6:8'>Rv 6:8</a>; <a href='B:730 20:3'>20:3</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of quantity <b>over, more than <a href='B:480 14:5'>Mk 14:5</a>; <a href='B:530 15:6'>1 Cor 15:6</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> of administrative position <b>over <a href='B:490 19:17'>Lk 19:17</a>, <a href='B:490 19:19'>19</a>; <a href='B:500 3:31'>J 3:31</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπανόρθωσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπάξας\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}